mapper.select: SELECT * FROM rgdb."DbV2002Fuka" AS 賦課Newest, (SELECT 賦課情報MAX通知書."choteiNendo" AS 調定年度, 賦課情報MAX通知書."hihokenshaNo" AS 被保険者番号, MAX(賦課情報MAX通知書."tsuchishoNo") AS 通知書番号 FROM rgdb."DbV2002Fuka" AS 賦課情報MAX通知書, (SELECT MAX("choteiNendo") AS 調定年度, "hihokenshaNo" AS 被保険者番号 FROM rgdb."DbV2002Fuka" WHERE "fukaNendo" = #{調定年度minus1} GROUP BY "hihokenshaNo" ) AS A WHERE 賦課情報MAX通知書."choteiNendo" = A."調定年度" AND 賦課情報MAX通知書."fukaNendo" = #{調定年度minus1} AND 賦課情報MAX通知書."hihokenshaNo" = A."被保険者番号" GROUP BY 賦課情報MAX通知書."choteiNendo", 賦課情報MAX通知書."hihokenshaNo" ) AS B WHERE 賦課Newest."choteiNendo" = B."調定年度" AND 賦課Newest."fukaNendo" = #{調定年度minus1} AND 賦課Newest."tsuchishoNo" = B."通知書番号" AND 賦課Newest."hihokenshaNo" = B."被保険者番号"
mapper.update: UPDATE rgdb."DbT2002FukaTemp" AS DbT2002FukaTemp SET "zennendoTokuchoKibetsuKingaku06" = (SELECT UrT0705ChoteiKyotsu."choteigaku" FROM rgdb."DbT2002FukaZennendoTemp" AS 前年度賦課 INNER JOIN rgdb."DbT2003Kibetsu" AS DbT2003Kibetsu ON DbT2003Kibetsu."choteiNendo" = 前年度賦課."choteiNendo" AND DbT2003Kibetsu."fukaNendo" = 前年度賦課."fukaNendo" AND DbT2003Kibetsu."tsuchishoNo" = 前年度賦課."tsuchishoNo" AND DbT2003Kibetsu."rirekiNo" = 前年度賦課."rirekiNo" AND DbT2003Kibetsu."ki" = 6 AND DbT2003Kibetsu."choshuHouhou" = #{徴収方法} INNER JOIN rgdb."UrT0705ChoteiKyotsu" AS UrT0705ChoteiKyotsu ON UrT0705ChoteiKyotsu."choteiId" = DbT2003Kibetsu."choteiId" WHERE 前年度賦課."hihokenshaNo" = DbT2002FukaTemp."hihokenshaNo" )
UPDATE rgdb."DbT2002FukaTemp" AS DbT2002FukaTemp SET "hihokenshaKubun" = #{被保険者区分} WHERE "koseigo_choshuHoho4gatsu" IN (#{特別徴収_厚生労働省}, #{特別徴収_地共済}) AND "zennendoTokuchoKibetsuKingaku06" != 0
